4. **SOLUTION:** Define f⁻¹ by f⁻¹(f(x))=x; bijection gives inverse exists and is unique.

5. **SOLUTION:** 13 people, 12 months ⇒ pigeonhole ⇒ two share a month.

6. **SOLUTION:** 28 students, 21 possible scores ⇒ two share a score.

